# c1
> openrouter:openai/gpt-image-1
@forward c2
@image -png output_{01..10}.png

Use the attached images as style/reference samples.
Create 10 new PNG images on transparent backgrounds in one consistent visual style.
Produce one output image per input image.
Preserve the semantic subject of each source image.
Do not merge all images into one sheet.

# c2
> claude.max
@file -markdown style_guide.md

Write a style guide for the image set generated by %from c1.
Describe line weight, palette, background expectations, naming, and rejection criteria.

# c3
> openai.fast
@file -json asset_manifest.json

Create a JSON manifest for the generated image artifacts from %from c1 and the guide from %from c2.
Use file names output_01.png through output_10.png and include a short description for each.
